block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This is Paper Plane 29 of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge. The Space Dart designed by Paul Jackson. This paper airplane is simple to fold and it flies really straight. This is an origami plane folded from a square sheet. Enjoy!!! If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 028 : Space Taxi by Kunihiko Kasahara", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/0uZDXBr2DbE Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
